These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, guinea-pig, rabbit
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the rabbit##7
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | cat | rabbit | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: kiwi, peas, broccoli, orange
1. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating orange##1
2. the person eating broccoli is somewhere between the person eating peas and the person eating kiwi##7
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating peas and the person eating orange##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | kiwi | orange | broccoli | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
