.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, boat, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere between the person driving the boat and the person driving the ship##7
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | boat | helicopter | airplane | ship |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, fantasy, western, horror
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching horror movies##2
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
4. the person watching mystery movies is somewhere between the person watching western movies and the person watching horror movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | western | mystery | fantasy | horror |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, canadian, french, italian
1. the chinese is somewhere between the italian and the canadian##7
2. the french is somewhere between the chinese and the italian##7
3. the french is on the left or right of the italian##3
4. the french is somewhere to the right of the italian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | italian | french | chinese | canadian |

